                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300527-180-victim1499 t18300527-180-viclabel964"></join>. I lost these articles on Sunday, the 2nd of May, from my premises, in <placeName id="t18300527-180-crimeloc965">Wood-street</placeName>
